┼In memory of
Dr Thomas Schofield
who worked in Queen Square from 2004-2010
All of old. Nothing else ever. Ever tried. Ever failed
No matter. Try again. Fail again
Fail better
(Samuel Beckett)"╦
╚~ Arthur Axford - Sunrise 1921 - D-Day Veteran 1944 - Sunset 2014 ~
Magical memories of fun & laughter, paintings & sunny times. Much loved Dad, Gramps & Special Friend, always smiling in our hearts."Ž
╠In Loving Memory
RONALD HALL                                             LOUISA HALL
25/11/1927           TRUE EASTENDERS       21/11/1930
  TO                                                                         TO
15/10/2003                                                       29/12/2007

Back Together Again
Their life together started the day they met by this lake,
So it seems only right to celebrate their lives by
placing this plaque here
DAD & MUM
If tears could build a stairway and memories a lane
I'd walk right up to heaven and bring ya home again
Luv Ya 124"▌
